column5: I don’t think Allison knew about the Stiles thing. Gerard kind of has his own secret plan and stuff that nobody knows about until the season finale.
The Unabomber (Ted Kaczynski). He was a domestic terrorist though.

You’re not alone, it’s currently happening to me as well. It‘s been going on ever since quarantine started and I hate these feelings so much. My boyfriend and I haven’t been able to see each other much lately (I’m immunocompromised) and it’s only making these moods worse. I really hope you get better and find some good advice! :)
